细一点？ 1213 补充：市面上有很多同质化的书籍，例如《数学分析》就有很多本，每一本都写得不详细。如果前赴后继把一本书写详细，那么就不存在工作量的问题，市面上有这一本书就足够了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-677252baea6043d3cda14ce6af4d8aee_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634381823"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvMW8i5z3g70GEAMaCTEwMzI1MjMxMyCVo9yrBjAAOPQJQAtyCTYzNDM4MTgyM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1712623041.572725", "card_id": "Q_31195477", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "保护珍稀动物是否符合进化论？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "进化论的思想是物竞天择适者生存，然而保护珍稀动物却为了生物多样性。这是否与进化论冲突？而且保护下来的动物大致上都会慢慢失去一些原始的机能（比如说领地，种群意识）。这是否是反进化论的行为"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/8de62afc1d4269db66616846506873d8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/31195477"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIvMW8i5z3g70GEAMaBzQ2NjA3OTQg/L3kqwUwADhYQAxyCDMxMTk1NDc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1712623041.574250", "card_id": "Q_423808394", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 601}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "羽毛球不会捡球就一定是菜鸡吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今天和同校的人约球，因为不会捡球就被说一眼就能看穿是菜鸡。但本人之前在本科学校打球也拿过校内比赛的名次，技术在女生中勉强能算中上水平吧，一直没有学习过用拍捡球。想问下这种观念是约定俗成的吗？还是说我确实应该学习下捡球。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6eb48a8b7852e66d434ff392d9c45c5f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color":